      "title": "Status of Tourists in Sri Lanka",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Foreign tourists are traveling by bullock carts in Pothuvil Arugambai area which is famous for tourism in Amparai district.",
        "In these difficult times when the country is facing economic crisis and fuel shortage, the arrival of tourists to Arukambai area in Pothu is increasing.",
        "Three-wheeler drivers ferrying tourists have also been affected due to fuel shortage. (R)"
      ],
